@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nsgchv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (v2 + 0.02)
    v2 = ((0.48 * 0.15) * wp.abs((tmp + 0.46 + v1 + 0.74)))
    v1 = (0.45 / 0.43)
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.sin((v2 + 0.25 + v0 + 0.62)))
    v0 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.44) + v1) / wp.abs((tmp + 0.97 + v0 + 0.08)))
    data[tid] = v0
